---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Power Automate Solutions | Julius Bruch"
    description="Automate your workflows with Cloud Flows, Desktop Flows (RPA) and more. Power Automate solutions by Microsoft 365 expert Julius Bruch."
>
    <main>
        <!-- Service Detail Section -->
        <section class="project-detail">
            <div class="container">
                <a href="/#services" class="back-link">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                    <span data-en="Back to Services" data-de="Zurück zu Dienstleistungen">Back to Services</span>
                </a>

                <div class="project-detail-content">
                    <div class="project-detail-header">
                        <h1 data-en="Power Automate Solutions" data-de="Power Automate Lösungen">Power Automate Solutions</h1>
                        <p class="project-category" data-en="Cloud Flows | Desktop Flows | RPA" data-de="Cloud Flows | Desktop Flows | RPA">Cloud Flows | Desktop Flows | RPA</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-detail-image">
                    <div class="image-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">⚙️</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-detail-body">
                        <h2 data-en="Service Overview" data-de="Leistungsübersicht">Service Overview</h2>
                        <p data-en="I design and implement automated workflows to connect your favorite apps and services. This includes syncing files, sending notifications, collecting data, generating PDF documents, and automating repetitive manual tasks using both Cloud Flows and Desktop Flows (RPA)." data-de="Ich entwerfe und implementiere automatisierte Workflows, um Ihre bevorzugten Apps und Dienste zu verbinden. Dazu gehören das Synchronisieren von Dateien, das Senden von Benachrichtigungen, das Sammeln von Daten, das Erstellen von PDF-Dokumenten und das Automatisieren wiederkehrender manueller Aufgaben mithilfe von Cloud Flows und Desktop Flows (RPA).">I design and implement automated workflows to connect your favorite apps and services. This includes syncing files, sending notifications, collecting data, generating PDF documents, and automating repetitive manual tasks using both Cloud Flows and Desktop Flows (RPA).</p>
                        
                        <p data-en="To guarantee reliability, all automations are built following professional Application Lifecycle Management (ALM) guidelines, including strict separation of development, testing, and production environments." data-de="Um Zuverlässigkeit zu garantieren, werden alle Automatisierungen nach professionellen Application Lifecycle Management (ALM) Richtlinien entwickelt, einschließlich der strikten Trennung von Entwicklungs-, Test- und Produktionsumgebungen.">To guarantee reliability, all automations are built following professional Application Lifecycle Management (ALM) guidelines, including strict separation of development, testing, and production environments.</p>

                        <h2 data-en="Licensing Information" data-de="Lizenzinformationen">Licensing Information</h2>
                        <p data-en="Power Automate has a flexible licensing structure depending on your automation complexity and data sources:" data-de="Power Automate verfügt über eine flexible Lizenzstruktur, die von der Komplexität Ihrer Automatisierung und Ihren Datenquellen abhängt:">Power Automate has a flexible licensing structure depending on your automation complexity and data sources:</p>
                        
                        <ul class="features-list">
                            <li data-en="Included in M365: Standard cloud flows triggered by standard apps (SharePoint, Outlook, Forms) are typically included for free in most Microsoft 365 plans." data-de="In M365 enthalten: Standard-Cloud-Flows, die von Standard-Apps (SharePoint, Outlook, Forms) ausgelöst werden, sind in den meisten Microsoft 365-Plänen in der Regel kostenlos enthalten."><b>Included in M365:</b> Standard cloud flows triggered by standard apps (SharePoint, Outlook, Forms) are typically included for free in most Microsoft 365 plans.</li>
                            
                            <li data-en="Power Automate Premium: For around $15 per user/month, this allows a user to run unlimited flows using Premium Connectors (e.g., HTTP requests, SQL, Dataverse)." data-de="Power Automate Premium: Für etwa 15 $ pro Benutzer/Monat kann ein Benutzer unbegrenzt Flows mit Premium-Konnektoren (z. B. HTTP-Anfragen, SQL, Dataverse) ausführen."><b>Power Automate Premium:</b> For around $15 per user/month, this allows a user to run unlimited flows using Premium Connectors (e.g., HTTP requests, SQL, Dataverse).</li>
                            
                            <li data-en="Power Automate Process: If an automated process operates independently of a specific user (e.g., a central organization-wide data sync), the flow itself can be licensed (approx. $150/bot/month)." data-de="Power Automate Process: Wenn ein automatisierter Prozess unabhängig von einem bestimmten Benutzer ausgeführt wird (z. B. eine zentrale organisationsweite Datensynchronisierung), kann der Flow selbst lizenziert werden (ca. 150 $/Bot/Monat)."><b>Power Automate Process:</b> If an automated process operates independently of a specific user (e.g., a central organization-wide data sync), the flow itself can be licensed (approx. $150/bot/month).</li>
                            
                            <li data-en="RPA Add-ons: Utilizing Desktop Flows for unattended Robotic Process Automation (controlling desktop UI without user intervention) requires additional unattended RPA licenses." data-de="RPA Add-ons: Die Verwendung von Desktop Flows für unbeaufsichtigte Robotic Process Automation (Steuerung der Desktop-Benutzeroberfläche ohne Benutzereingriff) erfordert zusätzliche Lizenzen für unbeaufsichtigte RPA."><b>RPA Add-ons:</b> Utilizing Desktop Flows for unattended Robotic Process Automation (controlling desktop UI without user intervention) requires additional unattended RPA licenses.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact CTA -->
        <section class="contact-cta">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 data-en="Ready to automate?" data-de="Bereit zur Automatisierung?">Ready to automate?</h2>
                <p data-en="Let's stop manual data entry and let the cloud do the heavy lifting." data-de="Stoppen wir die manuelle Dateneingabe und überlassen wir der Cloud die schwere Arbeit.">Let's stop manual data entry and let the cloud do the heavy lifting.</p>
                <a href="/#contact" class="cta-button" data-en="Get in Touch" data-de="Kontaktieren Sie mich">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>